(0, 'If you went back to {place} tomorrow, what would you do first?\n---\nPicture that first hour.\n• Drive a certain route, visit someone, eat somewhere\n• Or just stand in a spot and take it in\n• What would you hope to feel?', 'place', '{place}', 'return', 'event', '{has_places}', 'place_return', '{return,nostalgia}', 61),
