(0, 'What did living in {place} teach you about yourself?\n---\nPlaces shape us in ways we don''t always notice.\n• Patience, independence, a way of seeing things\n• Something you couldn''t have learned anywhere else\n• When did you realize it?', 'place', '{place}', 'growth', 'turning_point', '{has_places}', 'place_lesson', '{growth,identity}', 65),
