(2, 'What conversation with {person_name} do you replay in your head?\n---\nSome words stay on loop.\n• Comforting, confrontational, or unexpectedly honest\n• What was said, where were you?\n• Why does your mind keep going back?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'connection', 'people', '{has_contacts,answered_5+}', 'replayed_convo', '{connection,significance}', 231),
