(2, 'When has {person_name} laughed the hardest you''ve ever seen?\n---\nWatching someone come undone with joy is a gift.\n• A joke, a mishap, something absurd\n• What caused it, where were you?\n• What was it like to see?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'joy', 'people', '{has_contacts,answered_5+}', 'person_laugh', '{joy,humor}', 273),
