(3, 'Was there a part of your earlier story you held back?\n---\nSometimes we share the outline but not the heart.\n• A detail too raw, a person left out, a feeling skipped\n• What''s the rest of it?\n• Why did you hold it back?', NULL, '{memory_theme}', 'deeper', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'held_back', '{depth,honesty}', 351),
(3, 'What ordinary Tuesday from ten years ago would you relive?\n---\nNot a special occasion, just a day things felt right.\n• What made it ordinary?\n• What made it perfect?\n• Who was there?', NULL, '{}', 'nostalgia', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'ordinary_tuesday', '{nostalgia,specificity}', 352),
(3, 'What question do you wish someone would ask you?\n---\nSometimes the right question hasn''t arrived yet.\n• Nobody has thought to ask it\n• Or you''ve been waiting for the right person\n• What would your answer be?', NULL, '{}', 'unspoken', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'wish_asked', '{unspoken,longing}', 353),
(3, 'What quality or ability are you most afraid of losing?\n---\nNot a person, something about yourself.\n• Independence, memory, humor, ability to connect\n• What is it?\n• What does the fear tell you about what matters?', NULL, '{}', 'fear', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'afraid_losing_quality', '{fear,identity}', 354),
(3, 'What version of yourself did you leave behind to become who you are?\n---\nGrowth requires letting go.\n• The people-pleaser, the perfectionist, the safe one\n• Who were they?\n• Do you ever miss them?', NULL, '{}', 'evolution', 'turning_point', '{answered_10+}', 'former_self', '{evolution,shedding}', 355),
(3, 'What conversation do you keep almost having but never quite get to?\n---\nSome words stay right on the edge.\n• You start it in your head, then let the moment pass\n• Who is it with, what needs to be said?\n• What keeps stopping you?', NULL, '{}', 'avoidance', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'almost_conversation', '{avoidance,courage}', 356),
(3, 'Where does your mind go at two in the morning?\n---\nLate night thoughts reveal what we carry.\n• Worry, regret, planning, or something else\n• What comes to visit in the quiet?\n• How do you handle it?', NULL, '{}', 'introspection', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'late_night_mind', '{introspection,worry}', 357),
(3, 'What truth about your childhood took years to understand?\n---\nSome things only make sense with distance.\n• Didn''t have the context as a kid\n• Someone finally told you the real story\n• How did it change what you thought you knew?', NULL, '{}', 'childhood', 'turning_point', '{answered_10+}', 'childhood_truth', '{childhood,revelation}', 358),
(3, 'What''s the gap between who you are and who people think you are?\n---\nThe public version is never the full picture.\n• More confident, more together, simpler\n• What''s the gap?\n• What would it take for someone to see the full picture?', NULL, '{}', 'identity', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'public_private', '{identity,mask}', 359),
(3, 'What sacrifice did someone make for you that you can never repay?\n---\nSome debts can only be honored, not settled.\n• Time, opportunity, money, something less tangible\n• Who made it, what did it cost them?\n• How do you carry it?', NULL, '{}', 'gratitude', 'people', '{answered_10+}', 'unrepayable', '{gratitude,debt}', 360),
(3, 'What memory do you return to most often?\n---\nSome memories are magnetic.\n• Comforting, unresolved, or just pulls you in\n• What is it?\n• Has the meaning changed even though the facts haven''t?', NULL, '{}', 'recurring', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'most_revisited', '{recurring,interpretation}', 361),
(3, 'What have you worked hardest to forgive?\n---\nForgiveness is rarely a single moment.\n• A person, a situation, or yourself\n• How long has it taken?\n• Is it complete or still in progress?', NULL, '{}', 'forgiveness', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'hard_forgiveness', '{forgiveness,process}', 362),
(3, 'What part of your story shaped you more than anyone realizes?\n---\nThe biggest influences are often invisible.\n• Happened quietly, or you''ve never talked about it\n• What is it?\n• What would people understand differently?', NULL, '{}', 'hidden', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'hidden_shaper', '{hidden,influence}', 363),
(3, 'What stories do your hands carry?\n---\nLook at them right now.\n• What they''ve held, built, and how they''ve changed\n• What do they tell you about your life?\n• What would someone learn by looking?', NULL, '{}', 'reflection', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'looking_at_hands', '{reflection,aging,work}', 364),
(3, 'What would your younger self make of your life right now?\n---\nHonesty required.\n• Surprised, proud, confused, or relieved?\n• What would you tell them?\n• What question would they ask that''s hard to answer?', NULL, '{}', 'perspective', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'younger_self_view', '{perspective,assessment}', 365),
(3, 'What wound healed but left a mark you still feel?\n---\nNot physical, emotional.\n• A betrayal, a loss, a failure\n• The wound is closed\n• What does the scar remind you of when it aches?', NULL, '{}', 'scars', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'emotional_scar', '{scars,resilience}', 366),
(3, 'What''s the most important thing you''ve never said to someone still here?\n---\nSome words are always waiting.\n• The timing is never right, or they feel too heavy\n• What is it, who is it for?\n• What are you waiting for?', NULL, '{}', 'unsaid', 'people', '{answered_10+}', 'unsaid_living', '{unsaid,urgency}', 367),
(3, 'What pattern do you keep repeating even though you see it clearly?\n---\nAwareness doesn''t always equal change.\n• Relating to people, self-sabotage, a cycle\n• What is the pattern?\n• What''s underneath it?', NULL, '{}', 'patterns', 'turning_point', '{answered_10+}', 'repeated_pattern', '{patterns,awareness}', 368),
(3, 'What does loneliness actually feel like in your body?\n---\nNot the word, the sensation.\n• Maybe in your chest, your stomach, at a specific time\n• Where do you feel it?\n• What triggers it most?', NULL, '{}', 'loneliness', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'loneliness_sensation', '{loneliness,embodiment}', 369),
(3, 'What''s the most honest thing you could say about your relationship with your father?\n---\nNot the polished version.\n• Gratitude, resentment, confusion, or complicated love\n• What would that sentence be?\n• Why is it hard to say?', NULL, '{}', 'family', 'people', '{answered_10+}', 'father_honest', '{family,truth}', 370),
(3, 'What''s the biggest gap between your life from the outside and how it feels inside?\n---\nAppearances rarely match reality.\n• What do people assume?\n• What misses the mark?\n• What would surprise them?', NULL, '{}', 'perception', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'outside_vs_inside', '{perception,gap}', 371),
(3, 'What joy feels too fragile to talk about?\n---\nSome good things feel dangerous to name.\n• Afraid naming it will jinx it, too precious to expose\n• What is it?\n• What does protecting it cost you?', NULL, '{}', 'fragility', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'fragile_joy', '{fragility,superstition}', 372),
(3, 'What''s the most honest thing you could say about your relationship with your mother?\n---\nGo past the usual answer.\n• What would the deeper truth sound like?\n• What would she think if she heard it?\n• Why is it hard to say plainly?', NULL, '{}', 'family', 'people', '{answered_10+}', 'mother_honest', '{family,truth}', 373),
(3, 'What do you pretend doesn''t affect you that actually does, deeply?\n---\nSome impacts stay hidden on purpose.\n• A comment, a situation, something about how life went\n• What is it?\n• Why do you keep it hidden?', NULL, '{}', 'masks', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'hidden_impact', '{masks,vulnerability}', 374),
(3, 'What would you do differently if no one was keeping score?\n---\nNo judgments, no expectations, no audience.\n• What would you change, start, or stop?\n• Why haven''t you?\n• What would it feel like?', NULL, '{}', 'freedom', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'no_score', '{freedom,authenticity}', 375),
(3, 'What regret have you learned to carry without it crushing you?\n---\nSome regrets become companions.\n• Took years, still heavy sometimes\n• What is it?\n• How did you make peace?', NULL, '{}', 'regret', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'carried_regret', '{regret,acceptance}', 376),
(3, 'What moment from your life would you watch as a fly on the wall?\n---\nNot to change it, just to see it from outside.\n• To see your own face, or understand someone else\n• What would you watch?\n• What do you hope you''d see?', NULL, '{}', 'observation', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'fly_on_wall', '{observation,curiosity}', 377),
(3, 'What''s the hardest part about being truly known by someone?\n---\nIntimacy has a difficult side.\n• Losing hiding places, being seen on bad days\n• Fear that full knowledge leads to disappointment\n• What scares you about it?', NULL, '{}', 'intimacy', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'being_known', '{intimacy,fear}', 378),
(3, 'What are you still grieving that the world thinks you should be over?\n---\nGrief doesn''t follow anyone else''s timeline.\n• It''s been years, people stopped asking\n• What is it?\n• What does carrying it in silence feel like?', NULL, '{}', 'grief', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'ongoing_grief', '{grief,timeline}', 379),
(3, 'When did you have to choose between two options that both meant pain?\n---\nSome choices have no clean answer.\n• Two versions of loss\n• What did you choose?\n• What do you tell yourself about the other path?', NULL, '{}', 'dilemma', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'both_hurt', '{dilemma,impossible}', 380),
(3, 'What''s the most tender thing you''ve witnessed between two other people?\n---\nTenderness in others can move us deeply.\n• A parent and child, old friends, gentle strangers\n• What did you see?\n• What did it stir in you?', NULL, '{}', 'tenderness', 'people', '{answered_10+}', 'witnessed_tender', '{tenderness,beauty}', 381),
(3, 'What part of your body carries a memory?\n---\nThe body stores what the mind sometimes won''t.\n• Shoulders holding weight, hands remembering work\n• Where is the memory stored?\n• What does your body remember?', NULL, '{}', 'embodiment', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'body_memory', '{embodiment,somatic}', 382),
(3, 'What would you tell the next generation about what your era was really like?\n---\nNot the headlines, the texture of daily life.\n• The fears, the joys, the things nobody documented\n• What do you want them to know?\n• What would get lost without your telling?', NULL, '{}', 'legacy', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'era_truth', '{legacy,witness}', 383),
(3, 'What closed door do you sometimes wonder about opening again?\n---\nSome paths stay in our imagination.\n• A career, a relationship, a place, a version of yourself\n• What did you walk away from?\n• What draws you back?', NULL, '{}', 'roads', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'closed_door', '{roads,wonder}', 384),
(3, 'What does courage look like in your everyday life?\n---\nNot the dramatic kind, the quiet kind.\n• Having a conversation you dread, showing up\n• Being honest when it''s easier not to\n• What does your daily bravery look like?', NULL, '{}', 'courage', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'quiet_courage', '{courage,daily}', 385),
(3, 'When did you feel completely understood without having to explain?\n---\nBeing understood without words is rare.\n• Someone just knew, or a conversation clicked\n• Who was it, what was the context?\n• What did it feel like?', NULL, '{}', 'connection', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'understood', '{connection,relief}', 386),
(3, 'What would your life have been like if you had stayed in {place}?\n---\nThe road not taken is always vivid.\n• Different friends, career, sense of self\n• What do you imagine?\n• Better, worse, or just different?', 'place', '{place}', 'alternate', 'turning_point', '{has_places,answered_10+}', 'what_if_stayed', '{alternate,imagination}', 387),
(3, 'What''s the heaviest secret you ever carried for someone else?\n---\nOther people''s secrets have real weight.\n• They asked you, or you chose to protect them\n• How long did you hold it?\n• What did carrying it do to you?', NULL, '{}', 'burden', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'carried_secret', '{burden,loyalty}', 388),
(3, 'What version of love did you have to unlearn?\n---\nSome love models need replacing.\n• Love that looked like sacrifice, control, or disappearing\n• What was the old model?\n• What does the healthier version look like?', NULL, '{}', 'love', 'turning_point', '{answered_10+}', 'unlearn_love', '{love,growth}', 389),
(3, 'When did you surprise yourself with your own strength?\n---\nWe often don''t know what we can handle.\n• The moment demanded it\n• What was the situation?\n• How did it change how you see yourself?', NULL, '{}', 'strength', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'surprised_strength', '{strength,revelation}', 390),
(3, 'What do you need more of in your life right now?\n---\nBe honest with yourself.\n• Rest, connection, adventure, honesty\n• What''s standing between you and getting it?\n• Is the obstacle real, or could you move it?', NULL, '{}', 'needs', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'current_need', '{needs,obstacles}', 391),
(3, 'When did you have to choose between being right and being kind?\n---\nBoth feel important, but you can only pick one.\n• What was the situation?\n• Which did you choose?\n• Would you make the same call today?', NULL, '{}', 'compassion', 'event', '{answered_10+}', 'right_vs_kind', '{compassion,wisdom}', 392),
(3, 'What''s the most important thing about you that can''t be photographed?\n---\nSome things only show up in motion.\n• How you make people feel, your attention quality\n• Something about your spirit\n• What is it?', NULL, '{}', 'essence', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'beyond_photo', '{essence,spirit}', 393),
(3, 'What would {person_name} say if they could see who you''ve become?\n---\nSome reactions matter more than others.\n• Proud, surprised, full of questions\n• What do you imagine?\n• What would you want them to notice?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'legacy', 'people', '{has_contacts,answered_10+}', 'person_would_say', '{legacy,approval}', 394),
(3, 'When did you realize your parents had full inner lives separate from you?\n---\nThis discovery changes the parent-child dynamic.\n• They mentioned something from before you\n• Or you saw them in a purely personal moment\n• When did it happen?', NULL, '{}', 'family', 'turning_point', '{answered_10+}', 'parents_inner_life', '{family,maturity}', 395),
(3, 'What do you know about love now that you couldn''t understand at twenty?\n---\nExperience is the only teacher for some things.\n• Patience, showing up, choosing vs. wanting\n• What has time taught you?\n• When did the lesson land?', NULL, '{}', 'wisdom', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'love_wisdom', '{wisdom,experience}', 396),
(3, 'What moment of grace do you rarely talk about because it''s too precious?\n---\nSome things feel sacred.\n• Sharing might diminish it, protecting feels right\n• What was the moment?\n• What makes it sacred?', NULL, '{}', 'sacred', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'precious_grace', '{sacred,protection}', 397),
(3, 'What''s the truest thing you know about yourself?\n---\nNot flattering, not critical, just true.\n• Simply, undeniably true\n• What is it?\n• How long did it take to see clearly?', NULL, '{}', 'truth', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'truest_self', '{truth,identity}', 398),
