(3, 'What compliment do you struggle to accept even though you suspect it''s true?\n---\nSome truths are hard to receive.\n• Generous, creative, strong, and part of you deflects\n• What''s the compliment?\n• Why is it hard to let in?', NULL, '{}', 'self_image', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'hard_compliment', '{self_image,resistance}', 402),
