(3, 'What makes you feel most like yourself?\n---\nNot a role, not a performance, just you.\n• An activity, a person, a place, a state of mind\n• What is it?\n• When was the last time you felt it?', NULL, '{}', 'identity', 'feeling', '{answered_10+}', 'most_myself', '{identity,authenticity}', 418),
