-- place
(0, 'What''s a place from your past that still feels vivid?\n---\nPicture what made it feel like yours.\n• A room, a street corner, or somewhere outdoors\n• What sounds or smells come back when you think of it?\n• What would you find if you went back today?', NULL, '{}', 'travel', 'place', '{}', 'favorite_place', '{travel,nostalgia}', 1),
(0, 'What did your neighborhood look like when you were ten?\n---\nRecall the details only a kid would notice.\n• The sidewalk, the yard where everyone gathered\n• A shortcut only kids knew about\n• Who else was always around?', NULL, '{}', 'childhood', 'place', '{}', 'childhood_place', '{childhood,neighborhood,home}', 2),
(0, 'Where did you feel instantly at home, even as a stranger?\n---\nSome places just click the moment you walk in.\n• A city you visited, a friend''s kitchen, a lucky find\n• What was it about the place that felt right?\n• Did you ever go back?', NULL, '{}', 'belonging', 'place', '{}', 'unexpected_home', '{belonging,travel}', 3),
(0, 'Is there a place you keep meaning to go back to?\n---\nMaybe life got in the way, or you worry it changed.\n• What keeps pulling you back?\n• Are you hoping to find something, or someone?\n• What would it mean to finally return?', NULL, '{}', 'travel', 'place', '{}', 'return_place', '{travel,longing}', 4),
(0, 'Which building from your past would you walk through again?\n---\nA school, a grandparent''s house, a workplace.\n• Picture the hallways and the light\n• What did it feel like to move through that space?\n• Who would you expect to see inside?', NULL, '{}', 'nostalgia', 'place', '{}', 'building_memory', '{nostalgia,architecture}', 5),
(0, 'What road do you know so well you could navigate it blind?\n---\nA street you walked or drove a thousand times.\n• What did you pass along the way?\n• Who were you during that chapter?\n• Would you recognize it now?', NULL, '{}', 'familiarity', 'place', '{}', 'familiar_road', '{childhood,routine}', 6),
(0, 'Where were you the last time you felt truly at peace?\n---\nA porch, a beach, a chair, a quiet moment in your car.\n• What was the setting like?\n• What made it feel so still?\n• Could you find that feeling again?', NULL, '{}', 'emotion', 'place', '{}', 'peaceful_place', '{peace,retreat}', 7),
(0, 'What''s a place that doesn''t exist anymore but you can still picture?\n---\nA store that closed, a building torn down, a changed landscape.\n• What would someone miss who never saw it?\n• What made it special to you?\n• When did you last think about it?', NULL, '{}', 'memory', 'place', '{}', 'vanished_place', '{nostalgia,loss}', 8),

-- feeling
(0, 'What sound from childhood takes you right back?\n---\nSounds have a way of unlocking whole scenes.\n• A screen door, a song in the kitchen, someone calling your name\n• Where does the sound put you?\n• Who else is in that memory?', NULL, '{}', 'sensory', 'feeling', '{}', 'childhood_sound', '{childhood,sensory}', 9),
(0, 'What meal carries a whole story with it?\n---\nFood and memory are deeply linked.\n• Something a grandparent made, a dish from a trip\n• Who was at the table?\n• What was going on in your life at the time?', NULL, '{}', 'food', 'feeling', '{}', 'meaningful_meal', '{food,family,tradition}', 10),
(0, 'What scent drops you into a specific moment?\n---\nSmells transport us faster than anything.\n• Fresh cut grass, a perfume, something baking\n• Where are you when you smell it?\n• What''s happening around you?', NULL, '{}', 'sensory', 'feeling', '{}', 'smell_memory', '{sensory,nostalgia}', 11),
(0, 'When did something completely ordinary feel like enough?\n---\nContentment hides in simple moments.\n• Cooking, reading, walking, just sitting somewhere\n• What was the moment?\n• Why did it feel so right?', NULL, '{}', 'contentment', 'feeling', '{}', 'ordinary_joy', '{peace,simplicity}', 12),
(0, 'What makes you laugh every single time, no matter your mood?\n---\nSome things never lose their power.\n• A story someone tells, an inside joke, an old memory\n• Who''s usually there when it happens?\n• Why does it always land?', NULL, '{}', 'humor', 'feeling', '{}', 'reliable_laugh', '{humor,joy}', 13),
(0, 'What song locks in a whole era of your life?\n---\nMusic has a way of freezing a moment in time.\n• The radio during a road trip, on repeat during a season\n• Where does the song put you?\n• Who were you then?', NULL, '{}', 'music', 'feeling', '{}', 'song_memory', '{music,era,nostalgia}', 14),
(0, 'When did a stranger''s kindness stay with you for years?\n---\nSmall acts from unknown people can leave deep marks.\n• Someone who helped when you were lost\n• A few words you needed to hear\n• A tiny thing that made a big difference', NULL, '{}', 'kindness', 'feeling', '{}', 'stranger_kindness', '{kindness,gratitude}', 15),
(0, 'What feeling from childhood would you give anything to get back?\n---\nSome feelings belong to a certain age.\n• The freedom of summer, the safety of being carried\n• The excitement before a holiday\n• When did you last catch a glimpse of it?', NULL, '{}', 'childhood', 'feeling', '{}', 'childhood_feeling', '{childhood,innocence}', 16),

-- event
(0, 'What skill or knowledge of yours surprises other people?\n---\nEveryone has an unexpected talent.\n• Fixing something unusual, cooking something complex\n• How did you learn it?\n• Who, if anyone, taught you?', NULL, '{}', 'skills', 'event', '{}', 'unique_skill', '{skills,identity}', 17),
