(0, 'What''s the best unplanned day you''ve ever had?\n---\nThe best days are often the ones nobody scheduled.\n• Who were you with?\n• What unfolded?\n• Why does it stand out?', NULL, '{}', 'spontaneity', 'event', '{}', 'unplanned_day', '{spontaneity,joy}', 19),
(0, 'What tiny choice ended up steering your whole life?\n---\nSmall decisions can have enormous ripple effects.\n• Saying yes on a whim, turning down a different road\n• Talking to someone you almost didn''t\n• When did you realize it mattered?', NULL, '{}', 'decisions', 'event', '{}', 'small_decision', '{decisions,fate}', 20),
(0, 'What''s the hardest thing you''ve done that you''re glad you did?\n---\nSome of the best outcomes come from the toughest choices.\n• A move, a conversation, a commitment\n• What made it so hard?\n• What came out of it?', NULL, '{}', 'resilience', 'event', '{}', 'hard_but_glad', '{resilience,growth}', 21),
(0, 'What trip went completely sideways and became unforgettable?\n---\nThe best travel stories come from things going wrong.\n• A breakdown, bad weather, a wrong turn\n• How did it become an adventure?\n• Who was with you?', NULL, '{}', 'adventure', 'event', '{}', 'misadventure', '{travel,humor,resilience}', 22),
(0, 'What was the first big thing you did entirely on your own?\n---\nIndependence starts with one brave step.\n• Moving somewhere new, a solo decision\n• How did it go?\n• What did it teach you about yourself?', NULL, '{}', 'independence', 'event', '{}', 'first_solo', '{independence,growing_up}', 23),
(0, 'Why does one ordinary day stick in your memory so clearly?\n---\nNot a birthday or holiday, just a regular day.\n• Maybe it was the weather, the company, something subtle\n• What details do you still remember?\n• What made it different from any other day?', NULL, '{}', 'memory', 'event', '{}', 'vivid_ordinary', '{memory,detail}', 24),

-- people
(0, 'Who changed your life without even knowing it?\n---\nSome people shift your direction just by being themselves.\n• They introduced you to something, said the right thing\n• Or they modeled a different way of living\n• What did they set in motion?', NULL, '{}', 'influence', 'people', '{}', 'unknown_influence', '{influence,gratitude}', 25),
(0, 'What teacher or mentor said something at exactly the right time?\n---\nThe right words at the right moment can last a lifetime.\n• Who was it?\n• What did they say or do?\n• Why did it matter so much?', NULL, '{}', 'mentors', 'people', '{}', 'life_teacher', '{mentors,lessons}', 26),
(0, 'Who haven''t you talked to in years but still think about?\n---\nSome people stay in your head long after they leave your life.\n• A friend who moved, a coworker from another era\n• What do you wonder about them?\n• What would you say if you could?', NULL, '{}', 'lost_touch', 'people', '{}', 'lost_touch', '{longing,friendship}', 27),
(0, 'What''s the family story that gets told at every gathering?\n---\nEvery family has that one story on repeat.\n• Who tells it best?\n• Does it change depending on who''s in the room?\n• What''s the version only you know?', NULL, '{}', 'family', 'people', '{}', 'parent_wisdom', '{family,wisdom}', 28),
(0, 'Who is the funniest person you''ve ever known?\n---\nSome people just see the world differently.\n• Perfect timing, dry wit, a gift for absurdity\n• What did they do that cracked you up?\n• What was it like being around them?', NULL, '{}', 'humor', 'people', '{}', 'funniest_person', '{humor,friendship}', 29),
(0, 'Which two people from different parts of your life would you introduce?\n---\nA childhood friend and a coworker, a grandparent and a travel buddy.\n• Who would you pick?\n• What do you think would happen?\n• What do they have in common that only you see?', NULL, '{}', 'relationships', 'people', '{}', 'crossover_intro', '{friendship,connections}', 30),
(0, 'Who believed in you before you believed in yourself?\n---\nSometimes someone sees what you can''t.\n• They pushed you toward something\n• Or they just refused to let you give up\n• How did their faith land on you?', NULL, '{}', 'support', 'people', '{}', 'early_believer', '{support,confidence}', 31),
(0, 'What''s the best piece of advice anyone ever gave you?\n---\nGood advice echoes in your head for years.\n• From a parent, a stranger, a friend who knew you well\n• Did you take it?\n• How did it play out?', NULL, '{}', 'wisdom', 'people', '{}', 'best_advice', '{wisdom,decisions}', 32),

-- object
(0, 'What have you kept for years that others might toss?\n---\nSome objects carry meaning only you can see.\n• A ticket stub, a worn-out shirt, a trip memento\n• What would it tell someone about your life?\n• Why can''t you let it go?', NULL, '{}', 'keepsakes', 'object', '{}', 'kept_object', '{keepsakes,sentiment}', 33),
(0, 'What ordinary-looking thing you own holds a secret story?\n---\nThe best stories hide in plain sight.\n• Something on a shelf that carries a whole chapter\n• What is it?\n• What''s the story behind it?', NULL, '{}', 'possessions', 'object', '{}', 'story_object', '{possessions,stories}', 34),
(0, 'What book, movie, or album hit you in a way you didn''t expect?\n---\nSometimes art rearranges something inside you.\n• You picked it up casually and it changed things\n• When did you find it?\n• What did it stir up?', NULL, '{}', 'culture', 'object', '{}', 'unexpected_media', '{culture,surprise}', 35),
(0, 'Is there anything sentimental hiding in your wallet or bag?\n---\nCheck right now. You might be surprised.\n• An old photo, a note, something forgotten\n• How did it end up traveling with you?\n• What story does it carry?', NULL, '{}', 'everyday', 'object', '{}', 'pocket_sentiment', '{everyday,sentiment}', 36),
(0, 'What did you make with your own hands that still makes you proud?\n---\nThere''s something special about building things yourself.\n• Furniture, a meal for a crowd, a drawing, a repair\n• What does it mean to you?\n• Would you make it again?', NULL, '{}', 'creation', 'object', '{}', 'handmade_pride', '{creation,skills}', 37),
(0, 'What gift landed harder than the giver probably realized?\n---\nSome gifts show that someone truly sees you.\n• Perfectly chosen, arrived at the right moment\n• What was it?\n• Who gave it to you?', NULL, '{}', 'gifts', 'object', '{}', 'meaningful_gift', '{gifts,gratitude}', 38),
(0, 'If your house were on fire and everyone was safe, what would you grab?\n---\nOne thing, on your way out the door.\n• Something irreplaceable, or something that holds a feeling\n• What is it?\n• What would losing it mean?', NULL, '{}', 'priorities', 'object', '{}', 'fire_grab', '{priorities,sentiment}', 39),
(0, 'What piece of clothing takes you back to a specific time?\n---\nClothes hold memories like photographs do.\n• A jacket, a pair of shoes, a favorite shirt\n• What were you wearing?\n• What was happening in your life?', NULL, '{}', 'fashion', 'object', '{}', 'clothing_memory', '{fashion,era,nostalgia}', 40),

-- turning_point
(0, 'What turning point didn''t feel like one until years later?\n---\nSome changes are invisible in the moment.\n• A conversation, a move, a chance encounter\n• When did you realize what it actually was?\n• What shifted because of it?', NULL, '{}', 'reflection', 'turning_point', '{}', 'hidden_turning', '{reflection,hindsight}', 41),
