(0, 'When did you first feel like an adult?\n---\nThere''s usually a specific moment it hits you.\n• A responsibility you didn''t ask for\n• A decision no one else could make\n• How old were you?', NULL, '{}', 'growing_up', 'turning_point', '{}', 'first_adult', '{growing_up,identity}', 43),
