(0, 'Did you always know what you wanted, or figure it out along the way?\n---\nPurpose shows up differently for everyone.\n• Was there a moment of clarity?\n• Or has it been more of an unfolding?\n• Where are you with it now?', NULL, '{}', 'purpose', 'turning_point', '{}', 'life_direction', '{purpose,identity}', 45),
(0, 'What goodbye hit harder than you expected?\n---\nSometimes you don''t know what something means until it''s ending.\n• A person, a place, a chapter\n• What did it teach you about what you value?\n• Do you still feel it?', NULL, '{}', 'loss', 'turning_point', '{}', 'hard_goodbye', '{loss,love}', 46),
(0, 'When did you realize your parents were just people figuring it out?\n---\nThat shift changes everything.\n• They made a mistake, showed vulnerability, surprised you\n• When did it happen?\n• How did it change the way you saw them?', NULL, '{}', 'family', 'turning_point', '{}', 'parents_human', '{family,empathy,growing_up}', 47),
(0, 'What ended that turned out to be exactly what needed to happen?\n---\nSometimes the best chapter starts with something closing.\n• A job, a friendship, a chapter you didn''t want to lose\n• What opened up afterward?\n• How long before you saw it that way?', NULL, '{}', 'endings', 'turning_point', '{}', 'necessary_ending', '{endings,growth,acceptance}', 48),
(0, 'What risk did you almost not take?\n---\nThe best leaps often start with shaking knees.\n• Your stomach was in knots, people said don''t\n• What made you go through with it?\n• What happened on the other side?', NULL, '{}', 'courage', 'turning_point', '{}', 'worthy_risk', '{courage,decisions}', 49),
(0, 'What moment split your life into before and after?\n---\nSome events draw a clear line through everything.\n• A phone call, a diagnosis, a meeting, a decision\n• What was on each side of that line?\n• How did you carry yourself through?', NULL, '{}', 'milestones', 'turning_point', '{}', 'before_after', '{milestones,transformation}', 50);


