-- anchor='person' (16 prompts)
(0, 'When did {person_name} catch you completely off guard?\n---\nNot a planned surprise, just something unexpected.\n• A kindness, a confession, a side you hadn''t seen\n• What happened?\n• Did it change how you see them?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'relationships', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_surprise', '{surprise,character}', 67),
(0, 'What did {person_name} teach you without even trying?\n---\nPeople teach us things just by being themselves.\n• How they handled a hard moment, a habit you picked up\n• A way of looking at things\n• Do they know they taught you?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'lessons', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_lesson', '{lessons,influence}', 68),
(0, 'How would {person_name} describe you to a stranger?\n---\nIt says a lot about how they see you.\n• Something about your personality, a story they tell\n• Something you do that they find funny or endearing\n• Would they get it right?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'identity', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_describes_you', '{identity,perspective}', 69),
(0, 'What''s the funniest thing that ever happened between you and {person_name}?\n---\nThe kind of story you retell for years.\n• Something that went wrong, a misunderstanding\n• A moment that shouldn''t have been that funny\n• Does it still make you laugh?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'humor', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_funny', '{humor,bonding}', 70),
(0, 'What quiet moment with {person_name} keeps coming back to you?\n---\nNot a big event, just an ordinary one that stuck.\n• Driving somewhere, sitting at a table, doing nothing\n• What happened?\n• Why does it still matter?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'moments', 'feeling', '{has_contacts}', 'person_small_moment', '{moments,significance}', 71),
(0, 'What''s the first image that comes to mind when you think of {person_name}?\n---\nDon''t overthink it, just go with the first flash.\n• Their face in a certain light, a place, something they were doing\n• What do you see?\n• Why do you think that''s the one?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'memory', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_first_memory', '{memory,association}', 72),
(0, 'What''s something {person_name} does that''s just so them?\n---\nEvery person has something unmistakably theirs.\n• A phrase they always say\n• A gesture or habit you''d recognize anywhere\n• Something they do when nobody''s watching', 'person', '{person_name}', 'character', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_signature', '{character,identity}', 73),
(0, 'What day with {person_name} would you relive if you could?\n---\nA meal, a trip, a random Tuesday that was just right.\n• What made it so good?\n• What details do you remember?\n• Was it a holiday or just ordinary?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'experiences', 'event', '{has_contacts}', 'person_relive', '{experiences,nostalgia}', 74),
