(0, 'How did {person_name} help you through a hard time?\n---\nSometimes just being there is the whole thing.\n• They showed up practically, said the right thing\n• Or just stayed nearby when things felt unsteady\n• What did their presence mean?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'support', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_support', '{support,gratitude}', 77),
