(0, 'What side of {person_name} do most people never see?\n---\nClose relationships reveal hidden layers.\n• More tender than they seem, funnier in private\n• Or something heavy they carry quietly\n• What do you know that others miss?', 'person', '{person_name}', 'depth', 'people', '{has_contacts}', 'person_hidden_side', '{depth,perception}', 81),
