(0, 'You want to {why_text}. What made now the right time?\n---\nSomething tipped you from thinking to doing.\n• Was there a conversation that sparked it?\n• A feeling that had been building?\n• Something specific that happened?', 'why_here', '{why_text}', 'motivation', 'turning_point', '{has_why}', 'why_moment', '{motivation,decision}', 99),
