(0, 'What was the hardest part of starting to {why_text}?\n---\nMeaningful things usually come with surprises.\n• Something emotional, logistical, or personal\n• What caught you off guard?\n• How are you handling it?', 'why_here', '{why_text}', 'challenges', 'feeling', '{has_why}', 'why_challenge', '{challenges,honesty}', 106),
