(0, 'What did you believe at twenty that you''ve completely reversed?\n---\nOur convictions shift more than we expect.\n• About love, work, people, or yourself\n• What do you think now instead?\n• What changed your mind?', 'era', '{}', 'perspective', 'turning_point', '{has_era}', 'era_belief_change', '{perspective,growth}', 115),
