(0, 'What were you completely obsessed with when you were younger that you''d almost forgotten?\n---\nOld obsessions say a lot about who we were.\n• A hobby, a show, a person, a goal\n• What would your past self think of you moving on?\n• Does any of it still linger?', 'era', '{}', 'nostalgia', 'object', '{has_era}', 'era_obsession', '{nostalgia,passions}', 117),
