(0, 'Who were you trying to become when you were younger?\n---\nAmbition takes different shapes at different ages.\n• A clear picture, or just reaching for something unnamed\n• What were you chasing?\n• How close did you get?', 'era', '{}', 'ambition', 'turning_point', '{has_era}', 'era_ambition', '{ambition,identity}', 123),
